These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, siglo, fonseca, bongani
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goldfish, horse, fish
1. the fonseca-smoker is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the goldfish##2
2. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
3. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the owner of the horse##8
4. the owner of the goldfish is not the fonseca-smoker##6
5. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the blend-smoker##5
6. the blend-smoker is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Cigar   | bongani  | blend | fonseca | siglo  |
| Pet   | hamster | horse   | fish  | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, october, december, april
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, parkour, climbing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
2. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in october##2
5. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's sport is rowing##7
6. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
7. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | december | october          | april | march     |
| Sport    | climbing      | tennis | rowing | parkour |

