.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, collecting, magic-tricks
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, bellflower, tulip, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsmarigold is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby           | card-games | puzzles | collecting     | magic-tricks |
| Flower   | bellflower    | balloon-flower   | marigold | tulip    |

