.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
House: colonial, art-deco, modern, tower
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, turkish, colombian, french
1. the turkish is on the left of the french##1
2. the argentine is not to the left of the turkish##8
3. the colombian is on the right of the art-deco house##1
4. the tower house is not to the right of the colombian##8
5. the colonial house is the argentine##1
6. the colonial house is on the right of the colombian##1
7. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| House   | modern   | art-deco         | tower   | colonial    |
| Nationality         | turkish | french | colombian | argentine |

