.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, bike, car, quad-bike
City: new-york, berlin, hamburg, edinburgh
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the bike##7
2. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the helicopter##7
4. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person traveling to berlin##7
6. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
7. the person traveling to berlin is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
8. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | bike   | car | quad-bike | helicopter    |
| City         | new-york | edinburgh   | hamburg   | berlin |

