3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the victorian house##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
5. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5
6. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the modern house##8
7. the person who's sport is surfing is the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
