.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
House: tower, palace, townhouse, wooden
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, march, november, july
1. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the palace house##8
2. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the wooden house and the person who's birthday is in november##7
3. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
4. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
5. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the left of the palace house##8
6. the tower house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
8. the tower house is on the left of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| House   | palace      | townhouse | tower | wooden   |
| Birthday      | february | november | july  | march |

