2. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaisy##5
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere between the person who growslily and the fan of techno##7
5. the fan of soul is not to the right of the fan of reggae##8
6. the fan of reggae is somewhere between the person who growslily and the fan of soul##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Music-Genre     | techno | soul | reggae | disco     |
| Flower   | sunflower   | daisy        | rose          | lily |

