.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up, tea, juice
4 different games are played: canasta, poker, mah-jongg, bridge
1. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking juice and the person playing canasta##2
2. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
4. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
5. the person playing poker is the person playing poker##1
6. the person drinking tea is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
7. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
8. the person playing canasta is not to the left of the person playing poker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage   | juice   | mirinda | tea | 7up |
| Game     | bridge | poker       | canasta  | mah-jongg    |

