.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball, water-polo, tennis
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, domino, chess
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the right of the person playing chess##8
2. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
3. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5
4. the person playing scrabble is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person playing chess and the person playing domino##2
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Sport    | volleyball        | tennis | water-polo      | swimming    |
| Game   | scrabble | domino   | mah-jongg | chess |

