.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, time-travel, romance, animation
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, filmmaking, magic-tricks, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person watching crime movies##8
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person watching animation movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person watching time-travel movies##7
7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
8. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | time-travel         | romance    | crime       |
| Hobby      | filmmaking | video-games | singing | magic-tricks |

