.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, green, mauve, blood-red
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, alhambra, dannemann, bluemaster
1. the bluemaster-smoker is not to the left of the alhambra-smoker##8
2. the person who likes blood-red is in an odd position##4
3. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
4. the person who likes green is between the person who likes blood-red and the dannemann-smoker##2
5. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
6. the bongani-smoker is between the alhambra-smoker and the bluemaster-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Color   | azure     | green | blood-red        | mauve       |
| Cigar      | dannemann | alhambra  | bongani | bluemaster |

