.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, disco, electronic, classical
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, freelancer, scientist, project-manager
 1. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
 2. the fan of classical is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
 3. the fan of ambient is the scientist##1
 4. the scientist is not to the right of the freelancer##8
 5. the project-manager is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 6. the freelancer is somewhere to the right of the fan of electronic##5
 7. the freelancer is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the fan of ambient is not to the right of the scientist##8
 9. the freelancer is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8
10. the fan of disco is not to the left of the musician##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre          | disco    | electronic | ambient | classical |
| Job   | musician | project-manager  | scientist     | freelancer    |

