3. the person drinking 7up is the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is between the person drinking 7up and the person driving the taxi##2
7. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Transport    | taxi        | helicopter | boat | airplane |
| Beverage   | fanta | juice | 7up   | milk    |

