.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, freelancer, security-guard, analyst
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, cain, vegafina, old-henry
1. the cain-smoker is not the musician##6
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the analyst is not to the left of the old-henry-smoker##8
4. the security-guard is the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the analyst is somewhere between the cain-smoker and the ritmeester-smoker##7
6. the analyst is on the left of the musician##1
7. the vegafina-smoker is between the old-henry-smoker and the security-guard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Job         | freelancer    | analyst | musician | security-guard |
| Cigar   | cain | old-henry      | vegafina     | ritmeester     |

 